  <brief_title>Identification of Viral Variants Involved in the Transmission of Hepatitis C and Characterization of Antigenic and Functional Properties of Their Envelope Glycoproteins</brief_title>
  <acronym>VINTAGE VHC</acronym>
  <sponsors>
