  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study consists to Identify viral variants involved in the transmission of hepatitis C and
      characterize the antigenic and functional properties of their envelope glycoproteins at very
      early stage of infection (before seroconversion).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
